Package: lmc-ai-workstation
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: SKHLMC Debate Team
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-httpx, python3-websockets, python3-cryptography, ffmpeg, util-linux, iproute2, ufw, unattended-upgrades, gnome-remote-desktop, xdg-utils
Recommends: openssh-client
Description: SKHLMC AI Workstation Manager and outbound node
 Installs the localhost Manager GUI, outbound authenticated website node,
 health/power timers and allowlisted privileged helper. Large models, node
 credentials, Tailscale enrolment and GPT-SoVITS upstream are never downloaded
 by package installation.
